note:
I grew up in Humboldt County, lived in the Bay Area for eight years, then came home.
I've worked as a sign painter, graphic designer, illustrator and for many years now as a fine artist specializing in the natural world. I also love to sketch in pen and ink.
My travels have included Mongolia, Kenya, England, Germany, Italy and France.
My husband and I live on an acre in Dow's Prairie with our two rough collies and two cats.
